data.description: This beautiful end unit home has been lovingly maintained. Formal Living Room, Formal Dining Room and Eat-In Kitchen have newer flooring and have been neutrally painted. Kitchen features newer maple cabinets, countertops and Stainless Steel Appliances. Second floor has three generous sized Bedrooms and updated Bathroom. Master Bedroom and Guest Bedroom have newer carpeting and expanded double door closets. Third bedroom  has newer matching laminate wood flooring to hallway. All rooms have been neutrally painted as well. This home boasts lots of natural light and is situated on a quiet street to enjoy the covered front porch. Nice deck and fully fenced yard with a garden area.  Full Basement has a Laundry Area  and plenty of room for storage or could be easily finished for a Play Room or Entertainment Area.  Central Air and Electric were updated in 2015. Nothing to do but unpack your bags! This home is being sold As-is. Sale is contingent on seller finding suitable housing.
